n<br />\n每晚都會洗毛巾，但唔會分開洗，即係咩黎，大家明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過亦有餐廳紅邊加大窿布洗，藍邊分開洗既。</blockquote><br />\n其他我就唔知<br />\n不過我做果間我一定要求班crew分開<br />\n分番開紅邊藍邊 大窿<br />\n同埋啲盤一定會洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74cf1ec925b14dba7bace817429aa0129ba6509","tid":223600,"uid":11523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:33:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實每個月既公休都要大清潔 包括洗餐盤，洗飲品機，洗lobby,洗冰粒機，換濾芯(姐係平時係飲品機果啲免費水),洗廁所，洗廚房，洗爐  <br />\n<br />\n仲知乜Q都要洗<br />\n<br />\n利申：前紅牌員工,全部都做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n盤每日都洗<br />\n汽水機頭每日都洗<br />\nLobby唔洗講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冰粒機一個月一次<br />\nF1(汽水機filter)一季一次（唔好屌 跟規定）<br />\n廁所每日都洗<br />\n廚房 乜爐都每日洗兩次<br />\n新地機兩星期一次<br />\n水缸一年一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59c34c272cb92318196637e1a5d63f59935629b","tid":223600,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>D薯條hi到個盤邊<br />\n成日都好驚食到上一手既口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食左都唔緊要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有益架</blockquote><br />\n我成日奶的盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5445cda29aef59b8459d31ed562b128d4cd01e6","tid":223600,"uid":38386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:45:14.000Z","msg":"呢個post搞到我以後有d抗拒堂食M記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143b376a793c90a6ad9b75768787996d82dbd716","tid":223600,"uid":65975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:48:37.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔好掂到個盤<br />\n我以前做出面試過抹都冇抹"},{"pid":